{"tid":1170640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"協助台灣殺人案周浩鼎表示死者家屬希望可儘快修例 並認為歐盟意見偏頗 德國在發出錯誤信息攻擊香港法治","createTime":"2019-05-25T06:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T20:18:51.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"85aa4df85ba92ee20fbe08e5b6a5f87c0a48649f","tid":1170640,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:37:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190525/mobile/bkn-20190525130934845-0525_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190525%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190525130934845-0525_00822_001.html&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62B1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=aaccb990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190525/mobile/bkn-20190525130934845-0525_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n移交逃犯不應受政治影響 議員指死者家屬冀快修例<br />\n   <br />\n立法會內務委員會昨日(24日)通過撤銷《逃犯條例》法案委員會，並通過將修例下月交大會二讀辯論。協助台灣殺人案女死者家屬的議員周浩鼎表示，家屬一直有留意事態發展，冀可盡快通過修例。 <br />\n<br />\n對於台灣陸委會曾稱不接受以修例引渡台灣殺人案疑犯到台，周認為移交安排不應受政治影響，否則就不是一個專業及獨立的決定。另外，歐盟駐港代表發出照會，就修訂《逃犯條例》表達憂慮，周表示此舉是帶偏頗的政治宣示，又指德國向黃台仰及李東昇發出難民庇護，是向國際社會傳達錯誤訊息，令外界以為香港存在政治迫害。"},{"pid":"5db08fad0fb1f90854bf5ce53c4af95fce9206bd","tid":1170640,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf222da0a13f8f1a5caab023586d4f22d987764","tid":1170640,"uid":17641,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>通過咗又點，台灣唔肯收，你幫你個女斬撚死佢啊唔通</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b580932458d1b5de1c8bc4ff55c9f5ebfef68dfe","tid":1170640,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bf222da0a13f8f1a5caab023586d4f22d987764","tid":1170640,"uid":17641,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:39:53.00